constructor.details: The name/symbol are autogenerated.                                  For instance,                                  "Wrapped Ether" --> "Confidential Wrapped Ether"                                  "WETH" --> "WETHc".Do not use a small value in production to avoid security issues if the response                                  cannot be processed because the block time is higher than the delay.                                  The current implementation expects the Gateway to always return a decrypted                                  value within the delay specified, as long as it is sufficient enough.
